pinballux (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add automatic joystick GUID normalization for VPinball compatibility
  * Add DMD auto-positioning with one-click centering and sizing
  * Improved joystick configuration with SDL gamepad mapping
  * Resolution-aware DMD scaling for cabinet displays
  * Multi-monitor DMD positioning support

 -- Keith Phillips <keith@example.com>  Tue, 07 Oct 2025 12:30:00 -0500

pinballux (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Multi-monitor support for pinball cabinet displays
  * VPX table management and launching
  * Media integration with video, image, and audio support
  * Keyboard and joystick input handling
  * FTP media downloads from gameex.com
  * Setup GUI for configuration
  * Table Manager for media management
  * Automated VPinball download and installation

 -- Keith Phillips <keith@example.com>  Sun, 05 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000
